---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Dataset - Instrumetriq"
  description="Dataset notes for normalized public X (Twitter) post records and windowed summaries."
>
  <PageHero
    eyebrow="DATASET"
    title="Dataset"
    subtitle="Access and documentation for the Instrumetriq sentiment dataset."
  />
  <div class="pageContent">
    <section>
      <h2>About the Dataset</h2>
      <p>
        The Instrumetriq dataset consists of market snapshots combining price microstructure, spot sampling, and frozen social sentiment windows.
        A record is a single validated v7 snapshot (see <a href="/status">Status</a> for current counts).
      </p>
    </section>
    
    <section>
      <h2>Dataset Structure</h2>
      <p>
        The schema and file layout will be documented alongside the first public release.
        Until then, treat this page as a placeholder for format and access details.
      </p>
    </section>
    
    <section>
      <h2>Access & Licensing</h2>
      <p>
        Information about dataset access, usage terms, and licensing will be provided here.
        Public downloads will include a quickstart script for reading Parquet.
      </p>
    </section>
    
    <section>
      <h2>Citation</h2>
      <p>
        If you use this dataset in your research, please cite it appropriately. Citation
        guidelines will be provided here.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

